data.title: ONLINE VERSION
data.meta_description: Contains photographs and papers relating to the service of Lt John A. Doyle.
data.text:
Contains photographs and papers relating to the service of Lt John A. Doyle.

The 2nd Air Division Memorial Library also holds three silk escape maps in a bag donated by Steve Doyle: item no. 72 in their Memorabilia and Display Items collection. Memorabilia and Display collection inventory available on the Memorial Library's website: http://www.2ndair.org.uk [accessed 23 March 2011].
